race.description: Otl Over The Line Racing Handicap (C1)
race.comment: SUPREME STYLE (4) was backed from 1.45 into 1.30 and gave backers little cause for concern when resuming over 900m at Coonabarabran last start. Lightly raced mare who looks ready to fulfil her potential this prep. One to follow starting now. ROMANTIC LOVE (1) had a two-month let-up before a nice effort to finish third last time out over 1000m at Dubbo. Placed two from two at this distance. Has a tricky gate to contend with but if things go right he should be in the finish. SILVER CHAIR (6) was a month between runs when a tiring seventh at Muswellbrook recently. Should tighten up following that outing and an extra 100m helps. Can bounce back with the aid of the inside draw. ANDALE (3) last appeared when he easily won his maiden over 1300m at Narromine in June. Recent trial winner who looks primed for a positive return. HEFTY PRICE (13) drops back to his favourite distance today and is well treated after the claim.
